{"tid":1485902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在韓巴絲請入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:26:26.000Z","uid":514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"758eda1398ba5e191934798b8991a432d13bae04","tid":1485902,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"我之前喺一個集會入面識咗個韓國youtuber, 佢專門拍Anti China 嘅片，想藉此去令韓國人注意中國嘅威脅（之前聽佢講好多韓國政客都奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。佢話好多韓國人好佩服香港人直接對抗中共極權嘅勇氣，亦好支持香港人，同時見到黑警濫權濫捕亦好憤怒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊星期六首爾會有個反中遊行，到時佢會直播，佢想邀請在韓港人一齊出席，發表下睇法同感受。如果有在韓嘅巴絲可以出席，可以tg 聯絡：<br />\n@maskpackmantv<br />\n<br />\n呢個係佢youtube channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwb8Qy1su9_tOh1Mpl7YCoA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCwb8Qy1su9_tOh1Mpl7YCoA&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=ffba57f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwb8Qy1su9_tOh1Mpl7YCoA</a>"},{"pid":"8d6841c0cde8fcb47bc7335dc8ca2f3a97f87ca8","tid":1485902,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6bc8958066fa10884a1b5d22bd0033c9e94d8ce","tid":1485902,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ef01b016ff0c9cc3b907f3b5226c6516fe112ac8","tid":1485902,"uid":75647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:30.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c42d53f555f73403564c7981ae6f66b278f8533","tid":1485902,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a071503ee4bfc94b1cd1ad017c7f13a8076283db","tid":1485902,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,